sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant RT as ⚙️ Runtime
    participant PR as 📤 Producer
    participant KF as 📨 Kafka Topic
    participant C1 as 👤 Phase 1 Consumer
    participant RP as 🔄 Retry Policy
    participant C2 as 🔁 Replay Consumer
    participant CM as ✅ Commit Gate

    rect rgba(232, 245, 233, 0.5)
        Note over PR,C1: 📤 Produce & Deliver
        PR->>KF: [12:08:07] produce key-0 once
        KF->>C1: [12:08:07] deliver offset 0 to phase 1 consumer
    end

    rect rgba(255, 243, 224, 0.5)
        Note over C1,RP: 🔄 Retry Exhaustion
        C1->>RP: [12:08:12] attempt 1 fails
        RP->>C1: [12:08:12] retry with 100ms backoff
        C1->>RP: [12:08:12] attempt 2 fails
        RP->>C1: retry with 200ms backoff
        C1-->>KF: [12:08:13] retries exhausted, leave offset uncommitted
    end

    rect rgba(243, 229, 245, 0.5)
        Note over RT,CM: 🔁 Replay
        RT->>C2: [12:08:19] start replay consumer
        C2->>CM: [12:08:20] replayed offset 0 succeeds
        CM->>KF: [12:08:19] commit replayed message
    end
